ext4: Simplify ext4_writepage()

The actual code in ext4_writepage() is unnecessarily convoluted.
Simplify it so it is easier to understand, but otherwise logically
equivalent.

Signed-off-by: "Theodore Ts'o" <tytso@mit.edu>
---
